			<h1 class="heading-text">RESOURCES</h1>
      <p>Most of these resources are free although there are some books that I bought but you can find them pretty cheap second hand. All in all I estimate that I spent around £300 in total on resources (around £100 on books and £200 on a recurring Treehouse subscription).</p>
      <p>I've ordered the resources in terms of importance to my learning and how much I used them.</p>
